I am a doctoral researcher at the YuLab, Graduate School of Computer and Information Sciences, Hosei University. My work develops *AI*, *small / large language model (sLM / LLM)*, and *IoT* methods for the stability and resilience of *smart grids* and *IoT systems*, with a focus on time-series forecasting, spectral reprogramming, and graph-based control. All experiments run on dedicated multi-GPU servers I provision and maintain.

Outside research, I build production *AI / backend systems* and *full-stack web and mobile applications*, and work with partners across Japan, the Gulf, and West Africa.

== Research focus

- AI / sLM / LLM for power-system stability and grid resilience
- Spectral reprogramming of frozen *small language models (sLM)* and LLMs for time-series tasks
- *IoT* and edge intelligence for distributed energy resources
- Co-optimization of energy dispatch and communication routing
- Graph neural networks over electrical-grid topologies
- Federated learning, knowledge distillation across IoT-edge devices

== Engineering focus

- Production ML pipelines (training, inference, deployment) on *dedicated GPU servers*
- *IoT* data ingestion and edge model deployment
- Backend services in Python (Flask) and Node.js, with REST and GraphQL
- Data layers in MongoDB and SQL
- Full-stack web (React) and mobile (Flutter / Dart)

== Highlights

- *2 Q1 journal papers* in 2026 ([https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/internet-of-things Internet of Things], IF 7.6 / [https://www.sciencedirect.com/journal/expert-systems-with-applications Expert Systems with Applications], IF 7.5) on *IoT* time-series and *sLM*-based forecasting.
- *5 first-authored* IEEE flagship conference papers (VTC, ICUFN, ICCE, ICC).
- *★ IEEE VTS Tokyo/Japan Chapter 2024 Student Paper Award* at VTC2024-Fall, Washington D.C.
- Reviewer for /Theoretical Computer Science/ (Elsevier); Review Committee Member, IEEE ICECET 2026 (Rome, IEEE Italy Section).
- Validation of smart-grid co-optimization on benchmarks up to *2,869-bus PEGASE*, all on a dedicated GPU server.

